          "year": 2009,
          "note": "Bobby's first-ever date movie, age 13. Neither Sean nor Amanda can fully reconstruct the plot on the spot."
        },
        {
          "title": "Crazy Heart",
          "year": 2009,
          "note": "Jeff Bridges' overdue Best Actor win, after years of also-ran nominations."
        },
        {
          "title": "The Blind Side",
          "year": 2009,
          "note": "Sandra Bullock's Best Actress win, for a movie Sean says he doesn't think is very good."
        },
        {
